OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FWatch Kris Jepson's report on the
OL,7,FDisabled Ramblers trail around Kielder
OL,8,FForest
OL,10,FMembers of Disabled Ramblers have
OL,11,Ftaken to their mobility scooters to
OL,12,Fnavigate around Kielder Forest for the
OL,13,Ffirst time in 10 years.
OL,15,FUsing special mobility scooters called
OL,16,Ftrampers, they were able to ride over
OL,17,Fnewly accessible tracks on the
OL,18,FLakeside Way trail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
