OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FThe 6.5 mile route was the precursor
OL,7,Fto a larger event next year. Jonathan
OL,8,FClark, who arranged the event for the
OL,9,FDisabled Ramblers, said: "People will
OL,10,Fcome up here for a week long holiday
OL,11,Fand we'll prepare all the events for
OL,12,Fthat week, so they can be assured that
OL,13,Fthey can get to where they want to go,
OL,14,Fthey can get onto the trails and not
OL,15,Fbe hindered by steps and styles and
OL,16,Fgates."
OL,18,FFor those taking part, the access it
OL,19,Fgave them to the beauty of the forest
OL,20,Fwas unforgettable.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FOne man said: "Coming out on a ramble
OL,7,Fis great, because you meet so many
OL,8,Fother people as well, and it becomes a
OL,9,Fsocial activity. It's really life
OL,10,Fchanging having access to a place like
OL,11,Fthis. I would not be able to come down
OL,12,Fwithout the tramper."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FAnother said: "It's really brilliant
OL,7,Fto get out into the countryside and
OL,8,Fenjoy the fresh air and whatever, and
OL,9,Falso to help people who have got
OL,10,Fbigger problems than we have, and at
OL,11,Fthe moment, we both, we can manage the
OL,12,Fday between us with one of the
OL,13,Ftrampers. Without the tramper, we
OL,14,Fwouldn't be able to manage."
OL,16,FOne woman added: "I wouldn't be able
OL,17,Fto walk this distance, so it's really
OL,18,Flovely to be able to come on a walk
OL,19,Fwith my husband, doing the same thing,
OL,20,Fbecause usually I stay while he goes
OL,21,Foff walking."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
