OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FAnother said: "So I've been to Kielder
OL,7,Fwith my husband and my dog before and
OL,8,Fit's been heart breaking, because I've
OL,9,Fparked in the car and maybe walked 200
OL,10,Fyards and then I've had to go back to
OL,11,Fthe car, and watch them go off on
OL,12,Ftheir adventure over the horizon, so
OL,13,Fthis is absolutely brilliant."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
