CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FThe tracks have seen vast improvements
OL,7,Fover the past decade and that is part
OL,8,Fof a programme of accessibility
OL,9,Fenhancements across the forest.
OL,10,FForestry England's Alex MacLennan
OL,11,Fsaid: "We're working at the Kielder
OL,12,FCastle development and creating a
OL,13,Fchanging spaces for all room later
OL,14,Fthis year, and we've also got new
OL,15,Fadaptive cycles based at Team Cycles
OL,16,Fin Kielder, which means that users who
OL,17,Fhave mobility needs on bikes can also
OL,18,Fcome and enjoy Kielder."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1778186666
OL,3,CDisabled ramblers navigate Kielder
OL,4,CForest on mobility scooters
OL,6,FThe event has had much support from
OL,7,Flocal charities and businesses.
OL,8,FCalvert Kielder's Clive Gray said:
OL,9,F"The weather can be difficult and the
OL,10,Ftracks can be difficult, so we're
OL,11,Fincredibly supportive of getting as
OL,12,Fmany people out here as we can, having
OL,13,Faccess for all, whether disabled or
OL,14,Fnot, it's massively important to us."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
